HEADWORD: alphanumerical
<hw>alphanumerical</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>of or
pertaining to alphanumerics.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> alphanumeric, alphameric, alphamerical</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Computers)</fld> <def>using or consisting of only
alphabetical and numerical characters; -- contrasting with
<contr>binary</contr> or <contr>control</contr>.</def>
<illu><ex>alphanumeric</ex> characters</illu>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> alphanumeric, alphanumerical, alphameric,
alphamerical</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

